  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, saut\u00e9 until translucent.",
    "Stir in cumin, turmeric, and asafoetida. Cook for about 1 minute.",
    "Pour in cannellini beans and stir well to coat with spices. Cook for about 5 minutes.",
    "Fold in spinach leaves and coconut milk. Bring to a simmer.",
    "Simmer for another 2-3 minutes until the sauce has thickened slightly, adjusting seasoning if needed.",
    "Garnish with freshly ground black pepper before serving."
